<HistoricalDocument xmlns="http://example.com/historicaldocument">
  <Metadata>
    <Language>German</Language>
    <WritingDirection>ltr</WritingDirection>
    <PhysicalDescription>Parchment, 1 folio side, good condition.</PhysicalDescription>
    <Description>Excerpt from a historical chronicle or record.</Description>
    <Script>Latin</Script>
  </Metadata>
  <Page>
    <Header>
      <PageNumber>18</PageNumber>
    </Header>
    <Body>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>Der groff von swartzburg</Line>
        <Line>vnd sust all ander ritter</Line>
        <Line>vnd knecht wolten mit</Line>
        <Line>dar den ir was enteilvast</Line>
        <Line>siech usgenomen her Jacob</Line>
        <Line>von Hategart vnd hans</Line>
        <Line>von Letchenberg Ritter</Line>
        <Line>Die zeden werend gern</Line>
        <Line>mit mir gesin aber der</Line>
        <Line>patron wolt unser mit</Line>
        <Line>beiten So der merteil mit</Line>
        <Line>dar wolt vnd also musten</Line>
        <Line>wir mit grossem vnwillen</Line>
        <Line>dann̄ scheiden den wir</Line>
        <Line>mit dem patron vnd</Line>
        <Line>och den brüderen dar</Line>
        <Line>umb hattend ze zipren</Line>
        <Line>wachset dz zuker</Line>
      </Paragraph>
      <MarginalNote placement="right_margin">
        <Line>Saccharū</Line>
        <Line>in Cypro</Line>
        <Line>naseiti</Line>
      </MarginalNote>
    </Body>
  </Page>
</HistoricalDocument>
